---
title: Chicken Korma-Style Curry with Rice and Garlic Naan
description: This creamy cashew-based chicken curry could be just what you need! The mix of aromatics and spices combine in a velvety sauce that is hard to resist. And all on top of a fluffy bed of rice with a garlicky soft naan on the side – your stomach is going to be smiling!
